# Content Finder UI Rules

## Search Page Layout
- Large search input at top (hero-style prominence)
- Filter row: content type pills, year dropdown, format pills, exam selector
- Results below: card list, not grid (results need horizontal space for actions)
- Side sheet for preview (shadcn Sheet, right side, 500px)
- Search history chips below results

## Result Card Anatomy
- Left: content type icon (PDF=red, Web=blue, Questions=green, Syllabus=purple)
- Center: title (bold), source line (domain + credibility badge), snippet (2 lines), metadata badges
- Right: action buttons stacked vertically (Preview, Extract, Save)
- Credibility badges: Official=green shield, Established=blue check, Community=gray
- Match quality: colored dot before title (green/amber/gray)

## Extract Questions Flow (inline, below the result card)
1. Click Extract → show inline provider selector (compact)
2. Progress: "Extracting with Claude..." progress bar
3. Results: checklist of extracted questions
4. Each question: checkbox + Q text + 4 options (collapsed) + difficulty badge
5. Expand question to see full options + answer + explanation
6. Bottom: "Save X selected questions" button + "Select All" / "Deselect All"
7. After save: toast + card updates to show "15 questions extracted" badge

## Preview Sheet
- Header: title + source link (external) + credibility badge
- Body: rendered content (markdown for text, first pages for PDF)
- Footer: full-width action buttons (Extract Questions, Extract Syllabus, Download, Save)
- Close with X or click outside

## Saved Content Page
- Tab bar: All | Bookmarks | PDFs | Text | Questions | Syllabi
- Cards: title, source, type badge, date, exam badge, tags (editable inline)
- Actions: View (opens preview), Extract (if not done), Delete, Share
- Empty state per tab: "No saved [type] yet. Search for content to get started."

## Global Search Integration
- Compact search bar in dashboard top bar header
- On focus: expands width
- On submit: navigate to /dashboard/find?q={query}
- Find page reads searchParams.q and auto-triggers search on mount

## Loading States
- Search: skeleton cards (3) with shimmer animation
- Preview: skeleton text block in sheet
- Extract: progress bar with provider name
- Save: button shows spinner, then checkmark

## Mobile
- Filters collapse to "Filters" button → bottom sheet
- Result cards: full width, actions below content (not side-by-side)
- Preview sheet: full screen overlay
- Global search: icon only in header, expands on tap
